VDR Plugin 'newsticker' Revision History
-------------------------------------

2003-11-22: Version 0.0.1

- Initial revision.

2003-11-26: Version 0.0.2

- Now using wget
- Added support for local files

2003-11-26: Version 0.0.3

- Added an option to control the output folder

2005-01-01: Version 0.0.4

- Added support for VDR >= 1.3.17 (thanks to Thomas Günter)
- The colors of the ticker can be changed in the setup menu. (thanks to Zwer2k)